{
  "id": "5de9d347bb9cc20017bad3b6",
  "title": "楕円曲線",
  "created": 1575605067,
  "updated": 1575607344,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5de9d347bb9cc20017bad3b6",
      "text": "楕円曲線",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575605067,
      "updated": 1575605067
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9d34baff09e0000f8287e",
      "text": "[$ y^{2}=x^{3}+ax+b]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575605067,
      "updated": 1575605145
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9d38eaff09e0000f8287f",
      "text": " これを満たす(a, b)が群を成す、という説明は誤り",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575605135,
      "updated": 1575605183
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9d3bfaff09e0000f82881",
      "text": " \t無限遠点Oを足す必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575605183,
      "updated": 1575605556
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9d3ceaff09e0000f82882",
      "text": " \tこの無限遠点Oが単位元になるようにうまいこと加算を定義することで、群にすることができる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575605198,
      "updated": 1575605559
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9d429aff09e0000f82883",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575605290,
      "updated": 1575605353
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9d469aff09e0000f82884",
      "text": "うまい加算",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575605355,
      "updated": 1575605357
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9d46daff09e0000f82885",
      "text": "\t[$ s = \\frac{y_P - y_Q}{x_P - x_Q} ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575605357,
      "updated": 1575605416
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9d38eaff09e0000f82880",
      "text": "\t[$ x_{R} =s^{2}-x_{P}-x_{Q} ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575605135,
      "updated": 1575605458
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9d4bfaff09e0000f82887",
      "text": "\t[$ y_{R} =y_{P}+s(x_{R}-x_{P})]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575605439,
      "updated": 1575605470
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9d4b5aff09e0000f82886",
      "text": "\tこの加算はもちろんxP = xQの時にsの分母が0になってしまう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575605429,
      "updated": 1575605507
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9d503aff09e0000f82889",
      "text": "\t\tそこでその時には P + Q = O と定義する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575605508,
      "updated": 1575605579
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9d4eeaff09e0000f82888",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575605487,
      "updated": 1575605487
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9d5a7aff09e0000f8288a",
      "text": "この加算の定義にはaやbが含まれていない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575605672,
      "updated": 1575607145
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9db68aff09e0000f8288c",
      "text": "\tそのため「Pを受け取ってnPを返すオラクル」が存在した場合、任意の楕円曲線上の点PについてnPが得られる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575607145,
      "updated": 1575607222
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9dbb5aff09e0000f8288d",
      "text": "\t規格上は(P, nP)からnを作ることが困難な楕円曲線が選択されている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575607222,
      "updated": 1575607293
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9dbfdaff09e0000f8288f",
      "text": "\t\tしかし計算が容易な曲線上での(P, nP)を得ることができてしまう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575607293,
      "updated": 1575607309
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9dc0eaff09e0000f82890",
      "text": "\t\t渡されたPが想定した曲線上の点であるのかを検証すれば良いのだが、ほとんどのBluetoothデバイスは検証していない ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575607310,
      "updated": 1575607344
    },
    {
      "id": "5de9d5a9aff09e0000f8288b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575605674,
      "updated": 1575605674
    }
  ]
}